This spreadsheet, **"Instagram Content Automation Data(For Angela),"** serves as a central hub for managing and automating Instagram content. It tracks everything from product details and automation settings to content scheduling, performance analytics, and review logs.

Below is a detailed breakdown of each sheet's structure and the data it contains.

-----

### 1\. Logs

  * **Purpose:** Monitors and records every run of the content automation engine.
  * **Key Fields:** `Date`, `Status` (e.g., Success), `Feed Posts` (count), `Stories` (count), `Flagged` (items needing review), `Feed AI` / `Story AI` (models used), and `Timestamp`.
  * **Data Sample:**

| Date       | Status  | Feed Posts | Stories | Flagged | Feed AI | Story AI | Timestamp                |
| :--------- | :------ | :--------- | :------ | :------ | :------ | :------- | :----------------------- |
| 2026-03-03 | Success | 7          | 14      | 7       | openai  | openai   | 2026-03-03T10:46:17.368Z |

-----

### 2\. Config

  * **Purpose:** Stores the core settings and strategy for the automation, including brand voice, target audience, and posting schedules.
  * **Key Fields:** `brandName`, `tone`, `audience`, `contentPillars`, `Content Language`, `blacklistWords`, `min/maxCaptionWords`, `feedPostTime`, `morning/eveningStoryTime`, and `igAccessToken`.
  * **Data Sample:**
    | brandName | tone | audience | contentPillars | Language | Posting Hour |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | Beauty Media | Professional, supportive, expert | Beauty salon owners, spa administrators | Product Use Cases, Business Tips, Tutorials | German | 11:00 AM |

-----

### 3\. Product List

  * **Purpose:** A catalog of services and products available to be featured in generated content.
  * **Key Fields:** `ProductID`, `Name`, `Category`, `Description`, `KeyBenefits`, `ContentAngle`, `PreferredFormat`, `Price`, `Priority`, and `Status`.
  * **Data Sample:**
    | ProductID | Name | Category | Key Benefits | Price | Status |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | PROD-006 | Men's Haircut & Style | Service | Sharp look, professional appearance | From €40 | Active |
    | PROD-008 | Deep Tissue Massage | Service | Pain relief, improved mobility | From €90 | Active |

-----

### 4\. Analytics Dashboard

  * **Purpose:** Tracks the performance of published content and provides AI-generated recommendations for improvement.
  * **Key Fields:** `Topic`, `ContentType`, `EngagementRate`, `Likes`, `Reach`, `Ai recommendation`, and `PostDate`.
  * **Data Sample:**
    | Topic | ContentType | Engagement | Reach | AI Recommendation |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | 5 Italian Coffee Rituals | carousel | 12.5% | 5200 | (N/A) |
    | Deep Tissue Massage | carousel | 700% | (N/A) | Diversify content types, improve hooks... |

-----

### 5\. Story Remainders

  * **Purpose:** Manages the schedule and specific content for Instagram Stories, including interactive elements like polls and quizzes.
  * **Key Fields:** `ReminderDate`, `ReminderTime`, `PostTime`, `Day`, `StoryType`, `MainText`, `SupportText`, `InteractiveElement` (JSON format), and `Status`.
  * **Data Sample:**
    | ReminderDate | Day | StoryType | Main Text | Interactive Element |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | 2026-03-09 | Monday | Poll | Which service is most in-demand? | {"type":"poll", "options":\["Facial", "Massage"\]} |

-----

### 6\. Content Calender

  * **Purpose:** The master schedule for all upcoming feed posts and stories, containing full captions, media links, and review status.
  * **Key Fields:** `PostID`, `ContentType`, `Pillar`, `ScheduledDate`, `Topic`, `Hook`, `Caption`, `Hashtags`, `Status`, and `AISource`.
  * **Data Sample:**
    | PostID | ContentType | ScheduledDate | Topic | Status |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | IMG-20260309-001 | SINGLE IMAGE | 2026-03-09 | Men's Haircut & Style | pending |
    | CAR-20260310-001 | CAROUSEL | 2026-03-10 | Deep Tissue Massage | published |

-----

### 7\. Flagged Content

  * **Purpose:** A review queue for content that triggered specific quality flags (e.g., caption too short, blacklisted words) during generation.
  * **Key Fields:** `PostID`, `ContentType`, `ScheduledDate`, `ReviewFlags` (the reason for flagging), and `AISource`.
  * **Data Sample:**
    | PostID | ContentType | Review Flags | AI Source |
    | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
    | IMG-20260309-001 | single\_image | Caption: 28w | openai |
    | REL-20260311-001 | reel | Caption: 33w; No scenes | openai |

-----

### 8\. Content Archieve

  * **Purpose:** A historical record of past topics and hooks to ensure content variety and avoid repetition.
  * **Key Fields:** `Topic`, `Hook`, `ContentType`, `Pillar`, `ScheduledDate`, and `Hashtags`.
  * **Data Sample:**
    | Topic | Hook | ContentType | Pillar | Date |
